        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[kubectx + kubens: Power tools for kubectl]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://github.com/ahmetb/kubectx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">kubectx + kubens: Power tools for kubectl</a></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="install">Install<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/02/11/kubectx-kubens#install" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Install" title="Direct link to Install">​</a></h2>
<p><a href="https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/krew/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">krew</a>를 사용하여 kubectl 의 plugin으로 설치한다. 이 방식으로 설치하면 <code>kubectl ctx</code> 와 <code>kubectl ns</code> 형태로 사용한다.<br>
만약 shell completion scripts 로 사용하려면 <code>Homebrew</code>나 <code>apt</code> 등의 패키지 매니저로 직접 설치해야 한다.</p>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># kubectl plugins(macOS &amp; Linux)</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">kubectl krew install ctx</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">kubectl krew install ns</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># Homebrew</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">brew install kubectx</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">brew install kubens</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="kubectx">kubectx<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/02/11/kubectx-kubens#kubectx" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to kubectx" title="Direct link to kubectx">​</a></h2>
<p>다중 클러스터 환경에서 <code>kubectl</code>로 context를 편리하게 전환하기 위한 툴</p>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">kubectx &lt;k8s-cluster-context-name&gt;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># kubectx 명령어 실행 시 목록에서 context를 선택할 수 있음</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="kubens">kubens<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/02/11/kubectx-kubens#kubens" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to kubens" title="Direct link to kubens">​</a></h2>
<p><code>kubectl</code>에서 클러스터의 namespace를 매번 지정하지 않고 고정으로 지정할 수 있도록 하는 툴</p>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">kubectx &lt;k8s-namespace-name&gt;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># kubens 명령어 실행 시 목록에서 namespace를 선택할 수 있음</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>]]></content>
