        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[여러 머신에서 일관된 개발 환경을 사용할 수 있도록, personal configuration files(dotfiles, like ~/.gitconfig)을 관리하는 도구]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>여러 머신에서 일관된 개발 환경을 사용할 수 있도록, personal configuration files(dotfiles, like ~/.gitconfig)을 관리하는 도구</p>
<h1>Concept</h1>
<p>chezmoi는 dotfile을 <code>~/.local/share/chezmoi</code> 에 저장한다. 그리고 chezmoi apply 를 실행하면 각 dotfile 의 변경상태를 확인하고, 원하는 상태와 일치할 수 있도록 최소한의 변경 작업이 수행된다.</p>
<h1>Usage</h1>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="install-chezmoi">install chezmoi<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#install-chezmoi" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to install chezmoi" title="Direct link to install chezmoi">​</a></h3>
<p><a href="https://www.chezmoi.io/install/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.chezmoi.io/install/</a></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="chezmoi-설정-만들기">chezmoi 설정 만들기<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#chezmoi-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to chezmoi 설정 만들기" title="Direct link to chezmoi 설정 만들기">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="초기화-진행-localsharechezmoi에-dotfile이-저장되는-git-저장소-생성">초기화 진행. <code>~/.local/share/chezmoi</code>에 dotfile이 저장되는 git 저장소 생성.<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94-%EC%A7%84%ED%96%89-localsharechezmoi%EC%97%90-dotfile%EC%9D%B4-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-git-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%86%8C-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 초기화-진행-localsharechezmoi에-dotfile이-저장되는-git-저장소-생성" title="Direct link to 초기화-진행-localsharechezmoi에-dotfile이-저장되는-git-저장소-생성">​</a></h3>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi init</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="chezmoi를-통해-관리할-dotfile을-추가한다">chezmoi를 통해 관리할 dotfile을 추가한다.<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#chezmoi%EB%A5%BC-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%B4-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%A0-dotfile%EC%9D%84-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to chezmoi를 통해 관리할 dotfile을 추가한다." title="Direct link to chezmoi를 통해 관리할 dotfile을 추가한다.">​</a></h3>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi add ~/.zshrc</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="zshrc를-수정할-땐-edit-명령어를-사용한다">.zshrc를 수정할 땐 edit 명령어를 사용한다.<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#zshrc%EB%A5%BC-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95%ED%95%A0-%EB%95%90-edit-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to .zshrc를 수정할 땐 edit 명령어를 사용한다." title="Direct link to .zshrc를 수정할 땐 edit 명령어를 사용한다.">​</a></h3>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi edit ~/.zshrc    # $EDITOR에 에디터를 지정하여 다른 에디터로 수정 가능.</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="working-directory의-변경-사항-확인은-diff-명령어를-사용한다">working directory의 변경 사항 확인은 diff 명령어를 사용한다.<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#working-directory%EC%9D%98-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%EC%9D%80-diff-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to working directory의 변경 사항 확인은 diff 명령어를 사용한다." title="Direct link to working directory의 변경 사항 확인은 diff 명령어를 사용한다.">​</a></h3>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi diff</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="chezmoi의-변경-내용을-반영하고자-할-때는-apply-명령어를-사용한다">chezmoi의 변경 내용을 반영하고자 할 때는 apply 명령어를 사용한다.<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#chezmoi%EC%9D%98-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD-%EB%82%B4%EC%9A%A9%EC%9D%84-%EB%B0%98%EC%98%81%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%90-%ED%95%A0-%EB%95%8C%EB%8A%94-apply-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to chezmoi의 변경 내용을 반영하고자 할 때는 apply 명령어를 사용한다." title="Direct link to chezmoi의 변경 내용을 반영하고자 할 때는 apply 명령어를 사용한다.">​</a></h3>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi apply -v(verbose) -n(dry-run)</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="chezmoi-변경-사항을-git-저장소에-push">chezmoi 변경 사항을 git 저장소에 push<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#chezmoi-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD%EC%9D%84-git-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%86%8C%EC%97%90-push" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to chezmoi 변경 사항을 git 저장소에 push" title="Direct link to chezmoi 변경 사항을 git 저장소에 push">​</a></h3>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi cd</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git add .</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git commit -m "chezmoi config changed"</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git remote add origin https://github.com/kukuluku/dotfiles.git</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">git push</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="chezmoi-설정-불러오기">chezmoi 설정 불러오기<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/2025/01/25/chezmoi#chezmoi-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EB%B6%88%EB%9F%AC%EC%98%A4%EA%B8%B0" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to chezmoi 설정 불러오기" title="Direct link to chezmoi 설정 불러오기">​</a></h2>
<p>아래 명령어로 git에서 설정을 그대로 가져 올 수 있다.</p>
<div class="codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-text codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi init git@github.com:kukuluku/dotfiles.git</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi diff          # 가져온 설정이 어떤 변경이 있는지 확인</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi apply -v      # 가져온 설정을 로컬에 반영</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi edit [FILE]   # 반영 전 FILE 직접 수정</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi merge [FILE]  # FILE merge</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">chezmoi update -v     # 위 과정들을 한 번에 수행</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>]]></content>
