        <title type="html"><![CDATA[HashiCorp Nomad Review]]></title>
        <id>https://kukuluku.github.io/hashicorp-nomad</id>
        <link href="https://kukuluku.github.io/hashicorp-nomad"/>
        <updated>2025-01-24T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[HashiCorp의 오픈소스 서비스 스케줄러. 컨테이너 뿐만 아니라 비 컨테이너(바이너리, 배치 등) 워크로드 관리 지원.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>HashiCorp의 오픈소스 서비스 스케줄러. 컨테이너 뿐만 아니라 비 컨테이너(바이너리, 배치 등) 워크로드 관리 지원.
<a href="https://www.nomadproject.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.nomadproject.io/</a></p>
<h1>How Nomad Works</h1>
<img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/55680f28-f188-4f20-b078-f18311e8502c" width="70%">
<img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f12da6d2-a949-44e8-b0e1-58cd53d88ef8" width="70%">
<ul>
<li>Nomad의 기본 워크로드 단위는 Job 이다.</li>
<li>Nomad의 워크로드는 HCL(HashiCorp Configuration Language)로 기술 할 수 있다.</li>
</ul>
<h1>Key Definitions</h1>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="job">Job<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/hashicorp-nomad#job" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Job" title="Direct link to Job">​</a></h3>
<p>기본 워크로드</p>
<div class="language-hcl codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-hcl codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># This declares a job named "docs". There can</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"># be exactly one job declaration per job file</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">job "docs" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  ...</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="task-group">Task Group<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/hashicorp-nomad#task-group" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Task Group" title="Direct link to Task Group">​</a></h3>
<p>task의 모음으로, 하나의 동일한 client node에서 실행되는 단위. 여러 task group의 인스턴스는 다른 노드에서 실행 가능</p>
<div class="language-hcl codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-hcl codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">job "docs" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  group "web" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    # All tasks in this group will run on </span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    # the same node</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    ...</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  group "logging" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    # These tasks must also run together </span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    # but may be a different node from web</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    ...</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="task">Task<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/hashicorp-nomad#task" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Task" title="Direct link to Task">​</a></h3>
<p>가장 작은 단위의, 기본이 되는 단위</p>
<div class="language-hcl codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-hcl codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">job "docs" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  group "example" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    task "server" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      # ...</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="task-driver">Task Driver<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/hashicorp-nomad#task-driver" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Task Driver" title="Direct link to Task Driver">​</a></h3>
<p>작업을 실행하는 기본 수단(e.g. Docker, Java, Qemu..)</p>
<div class="language-hcl codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-hcl codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">task "server" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  driver = "docker"</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  ...</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="resources">Resources<a href="https://kukuluku.github.io/hashicorp-nomad#resources" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Resources" title="Direct link to Resources">​</a></h3>
<p>작업을 수행할 때 필요 사항을 명시하는 것</p>
<div class="language-hcl codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-hcl codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">job "docs" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  group "example" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    task "server" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      resources {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">        cpu    = 100</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">        memory = 256</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">        network {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">          mbits = 100</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">          port "http" {}</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">          port "ssh" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">            static = 22</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">          }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">        }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">        device "nvidia/gpu" {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">          count = 2</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">        }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">      }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h1>출처</h1>
<p><a href="https://medium.com/hashicorp-engineering/hashicorp-nomad-from-zero-to-wow-1615345aa539#9cc6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://medium.com/hashicorp-engineering/hashicorp-nomad-from-zero-to-wow-1615345aa539#9cc6</a></p>]]></content>
